---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 48
  - Title: Majjhima-nikâya
    Chapter:
      - I
      - Verse: 265
Tags:
  - Creation=Spiritual Paternity
---
On the conjunction of three things there is descent into the womb. As to this,
there must be coitus of the parents, it must be the mother’s season, and the
gandharva must be present. For so long there is conception.
